title: 1818 S Quebec Way #11-3 - Denver - 10 min from Cherry Creek Mall!
posting_body: ['TEXT', 'show contact info', 'NOW FOR MORE INFO!', 'VIRTUAL TOUR: 1818 S Quebec Way #11-3', 'AREA: DENVER!', 'FEATURES:', 'This townhome has 2 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, and ample amounts space!', 'Located nearby tons of shopping, tons of restaurants, and walking distance to the Cherry Creek Trail!', 'This unit also has a fireplace, balcony, and vaulted ceilings!', 'The community has a pool and hot tub!', 'INCLUDED UTILITIES:', 'Water and trash included.', 'TENANT PAID UTILITIES:', 'All other utilities not above paid by tenant.', 'BEDROOMS & BATHROOMS: 2 bedrooms (on the second floor) and 2 bathrooms.', 'KITCHEN APPLIANCES INCLUDED: Stove, refrigerator, dishwasher, and microwave.', 'LAUNDRY: Washer and dryer in unit.', 'FLOORING: Carpet.', 'HEAT/COOLING: Gas heat and central AC!', 'PARKING: 1 Car garage attached (on the basement floor).', 'FENCING:', 'N/A.', 'BASEMENT: Unfinished basement.', 'PETS: Pets considered with a one-time non-refundable pet fee of $250 per pet.', 'Sorry, but we cannot allow any of the following breeds of dog: American Pit Bull Terrier, American Staffordshire Terrier, and Staffordshire Bull Terrier.', 'SECURITY DEPOSIT:', "Security deposit is equal to one month's rent.", 'APPLICATION FEE: $30 per adult!', 'AVAILABILITY DATE: TODAY!', "**Applicants must be able to start a lease within 1 week of the property's listed availability date.", '**', 'LEASE TERM: Initial lease to end April through June of 2023 with 12-month extensions possible at that time.', 'Growing marijuana inside or outside the premises is not allowed, smoking of any kind inside the property is not allowed.', 'Minimum 700 credit score required.']
